==Ditiragalo=
Ka 2016, Mošireletši wa Setšhaba, Thuli Madonsela, o thomile nyakišišo ya go swarwa ga mmušo ka morago ga go amogela dingongorego tša semmušo go tšwa go Stanislaus Muyebe wa Dominican Order of Southern Africa, setho se sengwe sa setšhaba, le moetapele wa kganetšo Mmusi Maimane.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Collison |first=Carl |date=2016-10-20 |title=Friars fall out over public protector |url=https://mg.co.za/article/2016-10-20-friars-fall-out-over-public-protector/ |url-status=live |access-date=2021-12-13 |website=The Mail & Guardian |language=en-ZA}}</ref> Ka November 2017, go gatišwa ga pego ya nyakišišo ya gagwe, yeo e bitšwago State of Capture, go bakile kgobogo e kgolo. Pego e be e akaretša Zuma le bahlankedi ba bangwe ba mmušo ditswalanong tše di sa swanelago le lapa la Gupta, gare ga tše dingwe tše di sa swanego, gomme e šišinya gore Zuma e swanetše go kgetha khomišene ya dinyakišišo ka go thopša ga mmušo.Zuma o ile a nyaka gore dikutollo tša Madonsela di fetolwe ka Kgorong ya Tsheko, eupša kgoro ya tsheko e ile ya gana kgopelo ya gagwe, ya hwetša gore tšhišinyo ya Mošireletši wa Setšhaba e be e tlametše le gore Zuma o be a swanetše go kgetha khomišene ya dinyakišišo mo matšatšing a 30.<ref name=":14">{{Cite web |last=Gous |first=Nico |date=2018-01-09 |title=Zuma appoints commission of inquiry into state capture |url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/politics/2018-01-09-zuma-appoints-commission-of-inquiry-into-state-capture/ |url-status=live |access-date=2021-12-13 |website=Sunday Times |language=en-ZA}}</ref><ref name=":16">{{Cite book|last=Public Protector South Africa|url=http://www.saflii.org/images/329756472-State-of-Capture.pdf|title=State of Capture (Report No. 6 of 2016/17)|publisher=SAFLII|year=2017}}</ref> Ka taelo ya kgoro ya tsheko, e be e le Moahlodi yo Mogolo Mogoeng Mogoeng yo a kgethilego modulasetulo wa nyakišišo, Motlatša Moahlodi Raymond Zondo.<ref name=":12">{{Cite web |date=2018-01-09 |title=Statement by President Jacob Zuma on the establishment of the Commission of Inquiry into State of Capture |url=https://www.thepresidency.gov.za/press-statements/statement-president-jacob-zuma-establishment-commission-inquiry-state-capture |url-status=live |access-date=2021-12-13 |website=The Presidency |language=en}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.thepresidency.gov.za/press-statements/statement-president-jacob-zuma-establishment-commission-inquiry-state-capture "Statement by President Jacob Zuma on the establishment of the Commission of Inquiry into State of Capture"]. </cite></ref> Zondo o thušwa ke bahlankedi ba bangwe ba nako ka moka ba mmalwa, go akaretšwa yo e bego e le Auditor-General Terence Nombembe yo e bego ya le hlogo ya sehlopha sa dinyakišišo, le Frank Dutton, yo a hlanketšego bjalo ka monyakišiši yo mogolo go fihla lehung la gagwe ka Janaware 2022.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Du Toit |first=Pieter |date=2018-08-20 |title=The state capture inquiry: what you need to know |url=https://www.news24.com/news24/Analysis/the-state-capture-inquiry-what-you-need-to-know-20180819 |url-status=live |access-date=2021-12-13 |website=News24 |language=en-US}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Maughan |first=Karyn |date=20 January 2022 |title=Blow for Zondo, NPA as lead investigator on state capture matters dies |url=https://www.news24.com/news24/southafrica/news/just-in-blow-for-zondo-npa-as-lead-investigator-on-state-capture-matters-dies-20220120 |access-date=20 January 2022 |website=News24}}</ref>

Khomišene e hlomilwe ka Janaware 2018 eupša ga se ya swara tsheko ya yona ya mathomo go fihla ka Agostose 2018, ka nako yeo Zuma o ile a rola modiro gomme a tšeelwa legato ke Mopresidente [[Cyril Ramaphosa]].Ka morago ga lelokelelo la katološo, e phethile ditherišano tša yona ka Agostose 2021 ka bohlatse go tšwa go Ramaphosa.<ref name=":14">{{Cite web |last=Gous |first=Nico |date=2018-01-09 |title=Zuma appoints commission of inquiry into state capture |url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/politics/2018-01-09-zuma-appoints-commission-of-inquiry-into-state-capture/ |url-status=live |access-date=2021-12-13 |website=Sunday Times |language=en-ZA}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFGous2018">Gous, Nico (9 January 2018). </cite></ref> Le ge go le bjalo, ka la 29 Setemere, Kgorokgolo ya Tsheko ya Pretoria e dumeletše khomišene go katološwa gape ga dikgwedi tše tharo, yeo e fedilego mafelelong a Disemere 2021.<ref name=":13">{{Cite web |last=Ferreira |first=Emsie |date=2021-09-29 |title=High court grants Zondo commission a three-month extension |url=https://mg.co.za/news/2021-09-29-zondo-fifth-extension/ |url-status=live |access-date=2021-12-13 |website=The Mail & Guardian |language=en-ZA}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFFerreira2021">Ferreira, Emsie (29 September 2021). </cite></ref> Tona ya Toka le Ditirelo tša Toka Ronald Lamola o ikarabela ka go lefelela khomišene yeo e tlišitšwego, gomme a tlogela, tlhohlo ya semolao go kgopelo ya katološo.<ref name=":13" /> Khomišene e tšweleditše karolo ya boraro le ya mafelelo ya dikutollo tša yona ka March 1, 2022.

== Mafelo a kgahlego ==

=== Mantšu a tšhupetšo ===
Khomišene e be e kgethilwe ka tlase ga mabaka a tšhupetšo ao a ''bego'' a fetofetoga le maemo eupša a hlaotše ditaba tše mmalwa bakeng sa nyakišišo, kudu-kudu tšeo di tšwelelago go tšwa pegong ya State of Capture le maemo a go fapafapana a go lebanya. Ka gona khomišene e be e swanetše go nyakišiša ge e ba:

* Maiteko a be a dirilwe ka go hlohleletša maloko a khuduthamaga ya setšhaba goba bahlankedi ba bangwe ba mmušo, go akaretša ge e ba lapa la Gupta le be le file maemo a kabinete go boradipolotiki Vytjie Mentor le Mcebisi Jonas;
* go kgethwa ga maloko a khuduthamaga ya setšhaba le bao ba rwelego diofisi go be go utolotšwe go lapa la Gupta goba batho ba bangwe bao ba sa dumelelwego pele ga ge dikgetho di dirwa semmušo goba di tsebišwa;
* bahlankedi ba setšhaba goba ba mmušo ba be ba thušitše go fa ditheko ka ntle le molao ke mekgatlo ya mmušo go hola lapa la Gupta goba batho ba bangwe goba mekgatlo ya khamphani.
* go be go na le bomenetša ge go fiwa ditumelelano le ditheko ke mekgatlo ye megolo ye 21 ya mmušo yeo e lokeleditšwego ka go Šetulo 2 ya Molao wa Taolo ya Ditšhelete tša Setšhaba;
* go be go na le go se dumelelane le molao, go humišwa mo go sa swanelago, bomenetša goba tutuetšo ye e sa swanelago go fiwa ga ditumelelano, dilaesense tša meepo, papatšo ya mmušo ka kuranteng ya ''Mehla e Mefsa'', le ditirelo tše dingwe tša mmušo go lapa la Gupta;
* setho se sengwe le se sengwe sa khuduthamaga ya bosetšhaba se ile sa tsena ditaba tša go tswalelwa ga mafelo a panka a dikhamphani tša Gupta;
* baeletši ba bangwe le ba bangwe ka Lefapheng la Ditšhelete ba be ba kgethilwe ka ntle le ditshepedišo tša maleba, go akaretšwa ge e ba baeletši bao ba phagamego ba Tona Des van Rooyen ba be ba kgethwa ka mo go sa swanelago;
* go be go bile le bomenetša ge go fiwa ditumelelano le ditheko ke mmušo, le mohuta le bogolo bja mohuta ofe; le
* ka mo go kgethegilego, ge e le gore bahlankedi ba setšhaba goba bahlankedi bao ba bego ba na le tutuetšo ya go fiwa ditheko tša go ikhola, malapa a bona, goba mekgatlo yeo ba bego ba e na le kgahlego ya motho ka noši.

Ge go be go ka hwetšwa go se dumelelane le molao, Khomišene e be e swanetše go nyakišiša go fihla bokgoleng bjoo khuduthamaga ya setšhaba go akaretšwa Zuma le batlatšatona ba bego ba ikarabela ka bjona.
