==== Bohlatse ====
Go tloga ka la 16 Julae 2019, Zuma o hlatsetše pele ga Khomišene ya Zondo mabapi le tema ya gagwe go go thopeng mmušo le ditiro tša bomenetša. Letšatšing la mathomo la bohlatse bja gagwe o boletše gore go be go na le maano-mabe ao a thekgwago ke dinaga tša ka ntle kgahlanong le yena le gore ba bangwe ba bao ba bego ba hlatsela kgahlanong da yena e be e le dihlodi tša mehleng ya [[Apartheid|kgethologanyo]].<ref>{{Cite web |last=Chabalala |first=Jeanette |date=2019-07-16 |title=Zuma at state capture inquiry: Will he out more people? |url=https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/zuma-at-state-capture-inquiry-will-he-out-more-people-20190716 |access-date=2019-07-16 |website=News24 |language=en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Bezuidenhout |first=Jessica |date=2019-07-16 |title=The Essence of Zuma, Day One: 'State Capture Commission is designed to bury me' |url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2019-07-16-the-essence-of-zuma-day-one-state-capture-commission-is-designed-to-bury-me/ |url-status=live |access-date=2019-07-16 |website=Daily Maverick |language=en}}</ref> [[Jacob Zuma|Zuma]] o latofaditše Khomišene ya Zondo ka go ba sedirišwa sa go fediša mošomo wa gagwe wa dipolitiki. Zuma o dumetše gore o na le tswalano ya bogwera le barwarre ba Gupta, eupša o ganne go tšea karolo medirong le ge e le efe ya bomenetša.<ref name=":2" /> Ka morago ga letšatši la mathomo la bohlatse bja Zuma, Democratic Alliance e ile ya latofatša Zuma ka go leka go bapala mohlaselwa le go timetša khomišene.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Jacob Zuma attempted to play the victim at Zondo commission - DA's Mazzone {{!}} IOL News |url=https://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/jacob-zuma-attempted-to-play-the-victim-at-zondo-commission-das-mazzone-29248981 |access-date=2019-07-16 |website=Independent Online |location=South Africa |language=en}}</ref>

Letšatšing la bobedi la bohlatse bja Zuma, o boletše gore e be e le mohlaselwa wa maiteko a go ipolaya ka pomo, Tirelo ya Maphodisa a Afrika Borwa ka morago e boletše gore ba be ba sa tsebe gore tiragalo le ge e le efe ya go swana le ye e diregago.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Haffajee |first=Ferial |date=16 July 2019 |title=DAYS OF ZONDO: NEWSFLASH: Zuma hasn't laid a case related to suicide bomber plot – and reveals new assassination threat |url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2019-07-16-zuma-hasnt-laid-a-case-related-to-suicide-bomber-plot-and-reveals-new-assassination-threat/ |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=Daily Maverick |language=en}}</ref> Zuma o ile a latofatša leloko le legolo la ANC Ngoako Ramatlhodi ka go ba tlhodi yeo e akaretšwago ka go maano-mabe kgahlanong le yena.<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-07-16 |title=Zuma at Zondo - a blow by blow account of Day Two |url=https://www.biznews.com/leadership/2019/07/16/zuma-zondo-highlights-watch-live |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=BizNews.com |language=en-GB}}</ref> Letšatšing la boraro la bohlatse bja Zuma o ile a latofatša khomišene ka go mo kgetholla gomme a tšhošetša ka go tlogela tirišano ya gagwe.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Ntsabo |first=Mihlali |title=Zuma accuses Zondo of being unfair as testimony halted on day 3 |url=https://ewn.co.za/2019/07/17/zuma-accuses-zondo-of-being-unfair-as-testimony-halted-on-day-3 |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=ewn.co.za |language=en}}</ref> Letšatšing la bone, sehlopha sa molao sa Zuma se tsebišitše gore se tla tšwa go khomišene, eupša ka morago letšatšing lona leo se tsebišitše gore o fetotše monagano wa gagwe gomme o tla boa go tla nea bohlatse bjo bo oketšegilego ka letšatšikgwedi la ka morago.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Jacob Zuma retracts his withdrawal from state capture probe |url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/politics/2019-07-19-hlaudi-motsoeneng-sighted-as-jacob-zuma-arrives-at-state-capture-probe/ |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=TimesLIVE |language=en-ZA}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=19 July 2019 |title=Zuma will no longer participate in #StateCaptureInquiry - lawyer |url=https://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/zuma-will-no-longer-participate-in-statecaptureinquiry-lawyer-29495573 |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=Independent Online |location=South Africa |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web |date=2019-07-19 |title=Jacob Zuma backtracks on decision to withdraw from state capture inquiry |url=https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/jacob-zuma-backtracks-on-decision-to-withdraw-from-state-capture-inquiry-20190719 |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=News24 |language=en}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true">[https://www.news24.com/SouthAfrica/News/jacob-zuma-backtracks-on-decision-to-withdraw-from-state-capture-inquiry-20190719 "Jacob Zuma backtracks on decision to withdraw from state capture inquiry"]. </cite></ref>

==== Go nyatša kgoro ya tsheko ====
Ka morago ga bohlatse bja Zuma go khomišene, boraditaba ba Afrika Borwa ba ile ba šišinya gore kgonagalo ya gore Zuma a latofatšwe le go bonwa molato ka morago ka bosenyi bjo bo dirilwego nakong ya pušo ya gagwe goba ka go nea bohlatse bja maaka go khomišene e oketšegile.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Hogg |first=Alec |date=2019-07-15 |title=Zuma at Zondo: Odds shorten on another BRICs president behind bars |url=https://www.biznews.com/undictated/2019/07/15/zuma-zondo-another-bric-president-bars |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=BizNews.com |language=en-GB}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Mabena |first=Sipho |date=16 July 2019 |title=Zuma's allegations could see him facing jail time – analysts |url=https://citizen.co.za/news/south-africa/state-capture/2155177/zumas-allegations-could-see-him-facing-jail-time-analysts/ |access-date=2019-07-19 |website=The Citizen |language=en}}</ref> Ka la 11 Oktoboro 2019, kgoro ya tsheko ya Afrika Borwa e ganne Zuma go dira kgopelo ya go fediša ditatofatšo tše 16 tša bosenyi tša bomenetša, boradia le go hlatswa tšhelete tšeo di amanago le kgwebo ya dibetša ya $2.5bn (£1.98bn) yeo go thwego e dirilwe mafelelong a bo-1990 go netefatša gore madira a Afrika Borwa a itlhamilego a ka reka di-rand tše 30 tša didirišwa tša madira a Yuropa.

Sehlopha sa molao sa Zuma se ile sa leka go dira gore Moahlodi Zondo a ikarole go khomišene yeo e latofatšago Zondo ka kgethollo le go ba le segwera sa pele le Zuma.<ref name=":6">{{Cite web |last=Powell |first=Cathleen |title=South African judge has refused to step down from corruption probe: this was the right call |url=http://theconversation.com/south-african-judge-has-refused-to-step-down-from-corruption-probe-this-was-the-right-call-150484 |access-date=2020-11-27 |website=The Conversation |language=en}}</ref> Moahlodi Zondo o ganne kgopelo ya go gana.<ref name=":6" />

Dikgwedi tša ka godimo ga tše 16 ka morago ga ge Zuma a tšweletše la mathomo pele ga ge khomišene e ka latofatšwa ka bosenyi ka go tšwa khomišeneng ka ntle le tumelelo le go gana go nea bohlatse.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Mahlangu |first=Isaac |title=Zondo to lay criminal charges against Zuma for walking out |url=https://www.sowetanlive.co.za/news/south-africa/2020-11-23-zondo-to-lay-criminal-charges-against-zuma-for-walking-out/ |access-date=2020-11-27 |website=The Sowetan |language=en-ZA}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=Zondo commission to lay criminal charges against Jacob Zuma for walking out of inquiry |url=https://www.iol.co.za/news/politics/zondo-commission-to-lay-criminal-charges-against-jacob-zuma-for-walking-out-of-inquiry-01296852-383c-4a71-8f3d-c43c4fb50569 |access-date=2020-11-27 |website=Independent Online |location=South Africa |language=en}}</ref>  Se se be se dirilwe pele ga nako ye telele yeo ka yona Zuma a bego a leka go phema go tšwelela pele ga khomišene ka dikgato tša molao le dingangišano ka kholofelo ya gore khomišene e tla phetha pele ga ge a swanetše go tšwelela pele.<ref name=":4">{{Cite web |last=Naidoo |first=Lawson |date=2020-11-15 |title=OP-ED: Zuma vs Zondo: The former president's Stalingrad strategy in the arms deal saga is being replayed |url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2020-11-15-zuma-vs-zondo-the-former-presidents-stalingrad-strategy-in-the-arms-deal-saga-is-being-replayed/ |access-date=2020-11-27 |website=Daily Maverick |language=en}}</ref><ref name=":5">{{Cite web |last=Ntshidi |first=Edwin |title=Zondo commission must take action against Jacob Zuma for contempt - Outa |url=https://ewn.co.za/2020/11/22/zondo-commission-must-take-action-against-jacob-zuma-for-contempt-outa |access-date=2020-11-27 |website=ewn.co.za |language=en}}</ref> Mokgwa wo o be o bitšwa leano la tšhireletšo la Zuma la Stalingrad.<ref name=":4" /><ref>{{Cite web |last=AmaShabalala |first=Mawande |title=Yet another Stalingrad? Zuma unveils his latest weapon in his war with Zondo |url=https://www.timeslive.co.za/sunday-times-daily/politics/2020-11-16-yet-another-stalingrad-zuma-unveils-his-latest-weapon-in-his-war-with-zondo/ |access-date=2020-11-27 |website=TimesLIVE |language=en-ZA}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |last=Marrian |first=Natasha |title=NATASHA MARRIAN: Zuma's desperation in stalingrad |url=https://www.businesslive.co.za/fm/opinion/state-of-play/2020-10-01-natasha-marrian-zumas-desperation-in-stalingrad/ |access-date=2020-11-27 |website=BusinessLIVE |language=en-ZA}}</ref><ref name=":5" /> Ka Disemere 2020, Moahlodi Zondo o laetše Zuma go hlatsela pele ga khomišene mabapi le go akaretšwa ga Zuma ka ditirišanong tša kgwebo ya Guptas. Taelo ya Moahlodi Zondo e ile ya išwa Kgorong ya Molaotheo yeo e ilego ya ahlola gore Zuma o swanetše go araba dipotšišo pele ga khomišene gomme ya laela Zuma go lefa ditshenyagalelo tša molao tša khomišene.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Nicolson |first=Greg |date=2021-01-28 |title=NEWSFLASH: Final order: ConCourt rules Jacob Zuma must appear and answer questions at Zondo Commission |url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2021-01-28-final-order-concourt-rules-jacob-zuma-must-appear-and-answer-questions-at-zondo-commission/ |access-date=2021-01-28 |website=Daily Maverick |language=en}}</ref>

Zuma o ile a nyatša Kgorotsheko ya Molaotheo gomme a gana go nea bohlatse go Khomišene ya Zondo ka la 4 Feberware 2021. Khomišene, yeo taelo ya yona e felago ka la 31 Matšhe, e kgopetše kgoro ya tsheko taelo ya tšhoganetšo yeo e mo laelago go fa bohlatse. Moahlodi ka morago o ile a kgopela gore Zuma a nyatšwe molato wa kgoro ya tsheko. Ka la 25 Matšhe 2021, Kgorotsheko ya Molaotheo e ile ya thekga kahlolo ya peleng yeo e hweditšego gore go gana ga Zuma go nea bohlatse pele ga Khomišene go hlalošitšwe bjalo ka go nyatša kgoro ya tsheko. Ka la 29 June Kgorotsheko ya Molaotheo e ile ya ahlolela Zuma dikgwedi tše 15 kgolegong. Kapejana ka morago ga go golegwa ga Zuma ka la 7 Julae go ile gwa tsoga dikhuduego tše kgolo le bohodu diprofenseng tša [[KwaZulu Natala|KwaZulu-Natal]] le [[Gauteng]], go tloga ka la 9 go ya go la 17 Julae 2021.

== Dilo tšeo di hweditšwego ==
Mathomong dikutollo di be di swanetše go lokollwa ka dikarolo tše tharo eupša palo ye e ile ya oketšwa ka morago. E nngwe le e nngwe ya dikarolo tše mmalwa tša dikutollo tša pego e be e arogantšwe ka dibolumo tše mmalwa. Go ile gwa kgopelwa go katološwa gore khomišene e be le nako ya tlaleletšo ya go tliša dikutollo tša yona; se se ile sa šuthiša nako ya go lokolla dikutollo tsa yona ka moka go fihla ka la 15 June 2022.<ref>{{Cite web |title=Zondo asks for 6-week extension of State Capture Inquiry, Eskom report handover by Monday |url=https://www.polity.org.za/article/zondo-asks-for-6-week-extension-of-state-capture-inquiry-eskom-report-handover-by-monday-2022-04-22 |access-date=2022-04-30 |website=www.polity.org.za |language=en}}</ref> Khomišene e hweditše gore ditiragalo tše dintši tša go thopša ga mmušo di diregile ka gare ga dikgoro tša mmušo wa Afrika Borwa le dikgwebo tša mmušo nakong ya bopresidente bja Jacob Zuma bjalo ka ge bahlankedi ba bagolo ba be ba tshela molao ka mehla.<ref name=":23">{{Cite web |last=Bezuidenhout |first=Jessica |date=2022-01-04 |title=DAYS OF ZONDO: SOE contracts with Guptas’ New Age newspaper were unlawful, State Capture report finds |url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2022-01-05-soe-contracts-with-guptas-new-age-newspaper-were-unlawful-state-capture-report-finds/ |access-date=2022-01-05 |website=Daily Maverick |language=en}}</ref>

