=== Karolo 2: Transnet ===
Karolo 2 e ile ya gatišwa ka la 1 Feberware 2022 gomme ya tsebiša ka dikutollo tša bomenetša le taolo ye e sa lokago ka gare ga dikhamphani tša mmušo tša Denel, Eskom le Transnet. Dikutollo tše di latelago tše di lemogegago di dirilwe: 

* Jacob Zuma o be a nyaka gore Siyabonga Gama a kgethwe bjalo ka CEO gomme ka go realo a šoma bjalo ka "moemedi yo a ikemišeditšego" wa ditiro tša bomenetša go Transnet.<ref name="news24.com">{{Cite web |last=Wicks |first=Jeff |last2=Masondo |first2=Sipho |date=2 February 2022 |title=State capture report: Zuma should be investigated for Transnet corruption |url=https://www.news24.com/news24/southafrica/investigations/state-capture-report-zuma-should-be-investigated-for-transnet-corruption-20220202 |access-date=2 February 2022 |website=News24 |language=en}}</ref>
