* Ditirišano tše tharo tše kgolo tša bomenetša tša go reka ditimela tše 1,259 le China South Rail, China North Rail, General Electric le Bombardier Transportation.<ref name="Areff" />

* Brian Molefe, Anoj Singh le Siyabonga Gama ba swanetše go sekišwa ka baka la go nolofatša go reka ka bomenetša ditimela.<ref name="Areff">{{Cite web |last=Areff |first=Ahmed |date=1 February 2022 |title=Transnet locomotive procurement train smash: prosecute Molefe, Singh and Gama, Zondo says |url=https://www.news24.com/fin24/companies/transnet-locomotive-procurement-train-smash-prosecute-molefe-singh-and-gama-zondo-says-20220201 |access-date=1 February 2022 |website=News24 |language=en}}<cite class="citation web cs1" data-ve-ignore="true" id="CITEREFAreff2022">Areff, Ahmed (1 February 2022). </cite></ref>
