=== Karolo 3: Bosasa ===
Karolo 3 e gatišitšwe ka la 1 Matšhe 2022 gomme e lebišitšwe go dikutollo tše di amanago le bomenetša bjo bo amanago le konteraka ya mmušo ya poraebete BOSASA. Ka morago ga go lokollwa ga karolo ya 3 dikutollo tša khomišene di ile tša swawa diphošo ke bagwera ba Jacob Zuma.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Mafolo |first=Karabo |date=2022-03-02 |title=DAYS OF ZONDO, PART THREE: Zuma acolytes rubbish state capture report findings as ‘not worth the paper they are written on’ |url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2022-03-02-zuma-acolytes-rubbish-state-capture-report-findings-as-not-worth-the-paper-they-are-written-on/ |access-date=2022-03-02 |website=Daily Maverick |language=en}}</ref> Karolo 3 e dirile dikutollo tše di latelago tše di lemogegago le ditšhišinyo mabapi le tirišano ya mmušo le motšweletši wa ditirelo tša mmušo BOSASA:

* Radipolitiki yo a phagamego wa ANC Gwede Mantashe o swanetše go nyakišišwa ka baka la bomenetša ka baka la go amogela tsogo-le-kobong go tšwa go BOSASA.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Stone |first=Setumo |title=Zondo recommends Mantashe be probed for corruption |url=https://www.news24.com/citypress/politics/zondo-recommends-mantashe-be-probed-for-corruption-20220302 |access-date=2022-03-02 |website=Citypress |language=en-US}}</ref>
* Dudu Myeni o amogetše tsogo-le-kobong gomme a thuša go emiša nyakišišo ya BOSASA ya bomenetša.<ref>{{Cite web |last=Haffajee |first=Ferial |date=2022-03-01 |title=DAYS OF ZONDO, PART THREE: Dudu Myeni loved Louis Vuitton, especially when stuffed with R300,000 Bosasa cash |url=https://www.dailymaverick.co.za/article/2022-03-02-dudu-myeni-loved-louis-vuitton-especially-when-stuffed-with-r300000-bosasa-cash/ |access-date=2022-03-02 |website=Daily Maverick |language=en}}</ref>

Karolo 4 ya dikutollo tša khomišene e be e arogantšwe ka dibolumo tše nne gomme ya gatišwa mesong ya 29 April 2022. Karolo ya bone ya dikutollo e be e lebišitšwe go go leka go thopa Letlotlo la Setšhaba, bomenetša magareng ga motšweletši wa ditirelo tša thekinolotši ya poraebete EOH le Motse wa Johannesburg, bomenetšo ka gare ga khamphani ya meepo ya ditaamane ya mmušo Alexkor, Free State asbestos le porojeke ya go tloša asbestos ya setšhaba, le go thopa tirelo ya mohlagase ya mmušo Eskom. Karolo ya bone ya pego ya dikomiti e dirile dikutollo tše di latelago tše di lemogegago:

* Porojeke ya R1.2 billion Free State Housing ya go aga dintlo tše 200,000 e be e le "go palelwa mo go nyamišago" ka lebaka la go se laole gabotse ga mmušo.<ref name=":26" /><ref name=":26">{{Cite web |last=Khoza |first=Amanda |title=Part 4 of state capture report notes ‘dismal failure’ of Free State’s R1bn housing project |url=https://www.businesslive.co.za/bd/national/2022-04-29-part-4-of-state-capture-report-notes-dismal-failure-of-free-states-r1bn-housing-project/ |access-date=2022-04-29 |website=BusinessLIVE |language=en-ZA}}</ref>
